{
  "title": "Claude Code - MCP Servers",
  "uid": "claude-code-mcp",
  "tags": [
    "claude-code",
    "mcp"
  ],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-7d",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "team",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prom-claude-code"
        },
        "query": "label_values(claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total, team)",
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "MCP Server Connections (1h)",
      "description": "Loki mcp_server_connection 事件数,代表 Claude 启动了 stdio 握手多少次",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki-claude-code"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service_name=\"claude-code\"} |= `mcp_server_connection` [1h]))"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "MCP Tool Calls (1h)",
      "description": "tool_name='mcp_tool' 事件数。Claude 2.1.153 真实 server/tool 在 tool_parameters JSON label 里",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki-claude-code"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service_name=\"claude-code\"} | event_name=\"tool_result\" | tool_name=\"mcp_tool\" [1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{tool_name}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "mcp_tool"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "green"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.displayMode",
                "value": "color-background"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Top MCP Server (1h)",
      "description": "1h 内连接次数最多的 MCP server。注意: Claude 2.1.153 不会重复连同一个 server(连接是 lazy 的,常驻),所以'次数' ≈ 配置里的 server 数 × Claude 重启次数",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki-claude-code"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(1, sum by (server_name) (count_over_time({service_name=\"claude-code\"} |= `mcp_server_connection` [1h])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{server_name}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total MCP Cost (USD)",
      "description": "所有 MCP 调用总成本。Claude 2.1.153 把绝大多数 MCP 调用的 mcp_server_name 都标 'custom' (实测),所以按 server 拆不出来,只能看总量",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-claude-code"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 18,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total{mcp_server_name!=\"\", team=~\"$team\"})"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 4
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "MCP Server Connection Count (1h)",
      "description": "按 server_name 拆连接次数。健康度指标: 反复连接 = 客户端在重启 MCP 进程,可能配置有问题",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki-claude-code"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (server_name) (count_over_time({service_name=\"claude-code\"} |= `mcp_server_connection` [1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{server_name}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "displayMode": "gradient",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "showUnfilled": true
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {
            "mode": "continuous-purples"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "MCP Cost (single 'custom' bucket, 2.1.153 limitation)",
      "description": "Claude 2.1.153 实测: Prom 端 mcp_server_name 永远 = 'custom',不按 server 拆。换一个角度看 MCP 的成本:按 model 拆(mcp_tool 调用的主模型)或者按 user 拆",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-claude-code"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 5,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (mcp_tool_name) (claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total{mcp_server_name!=\"\", mcp_server_name=\"custom\", team=~\"$team\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{mcp_tool_name}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "displayMode": "gradient",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "showUnfilled": true
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 4,
          "color": {
            "mode": "continuous-YlRd"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Recent MCP Tool Calls (raw stream)",
      "description": "mcp_tool 调用的原始事件。展开 row 看 tool_parameters JSON label 拿 mcp_server_name + mcp_tool_name 真实值",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki-claude-code"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 29,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 14
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "{service_name=\"claude-code\"} | event_name=\"tool_result\" | tool_name=\"mcp_tool\"",
          "legendFormat": "{{tool_name}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "showLabels": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "showCommonLabels": false,
        "prettifyLogMessage": true,
        "dedupStrategy": "none"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "MCP 连接状态分布 (connected / failed / disconnected)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki-claude-code"
      },
      "description": "来自 mcp_server_connection 的 status。⚠️ 实测 failed 往往 ≥ connected —— 这是过去被'连接次数'掩盖的关键健康信号。",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 13
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by(status)(count_over_time({service_name=\"claude-code\"} | event_name=\"mcp_server_connection\" [$__range]))",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki-claude-code"
          },
          "queryType": "instant",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false,
          "legendFormat": "{{status}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "noValue": "无数据"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "connected"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "green"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "failed"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "red"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "disconnected"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "orange"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "pieType": "donut",
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "values": [
            "value",
            "percent"
          ]
        },
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "连接失败的 Server 排行 (status=failed)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki-claude-code"
      },
      "description": "哪些 MCP server 在掉线/握手失败。实测集中在远程 sse server(n8n-mcp / grafana / helixops / victoria*)。是 MCP 配置/网络排障的直接入口。",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 10,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 13
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by(server_name)(count_over_time({service_name=\"claude-code\"} | event_name=\"mcp_server_connection\" | status=\"failed\" | server_name!=\"\" [$__range]))",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki-claude-code"
          },
          "queryType": "instant",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false,
          "legendFormat": "{{server_name}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {
            "mode": "continuous-YlRd"
          },
          "noValue": "区间内无连接失败 ✓"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "displayMode": "gradient",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "showUnfilled": true,
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "连接按 Transport 分布 (stdio / sse / proxy)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki-claude-code"
      },
      "description": "stdio(本地进程) vs sse/claudeai-proxy(远程)。失败几乎全在远程 transport,此图佐证'远程 MCP 不稳定'。",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 13
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by(transport_type)(count_over_time({service_name=\"claude-code\"} | event_name=\"mcp_server_connection\" [$__range]))",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki-claude-code"
          },
          "queryType": "instant",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false,
          "legendFormat": "{{transport_type}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "noValue": "无数据"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "pieType": "donut",
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "values": [
            "value",
            "percent"
          ]
        },
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "MCP 握手延迟 (avg duration_ms by server)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki-claude-code"
      },
      "description": "各 server 连接握手平均耗时。慢连接(如 ide/context7/Google Drive 数秒级)拖慢启动。",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 21
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "avg by(server_name)(avg_over_time({service_name=\"claude-code\"} | event_name=\"mcp_server_connection\" | server_name!=\"\" | unwrap duration_ms [$__range]))",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki-claude-code"
          },
          "queryType": "instant",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false,
          "legendFormat": "{{server_name}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "decimals": 0,
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 1000
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 5000
              }
            ]
          },
          "noValue": "无数据"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "displayMode": "lcd",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "showUnfilled": true,
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "links": [
    {
      "asDropdown": true,
      "icon": "apps",
      "includeVars": true,
      "keepTime": true,
      "tags": [
        "claude-code"
      ],
      "targetBlank": false,
      "title": "📊 Claude Code 面板",
      "type": "dashboards"
    }
  ]
}